{"comments":"FontVariation - OpenType variable font axis settings.\n\nVariable fonts contain multiple styles along continuous axes.\nThis module provides type-safe access to standard and custom axes.\n\n## Registered Axes (4-letter lowercase tags)\n- wght: Weight (same as CSS font-weight)\n- wdth: Width (same as CSS font-stretch)\n- slnt: Slant (oblique angle in degrees)\n- ital: Italic (0 = upright, 1 = italic)\n- opsz: Optical size (matches font size in points)\n\n## Custom Axes (4-letter uppercase tags)\n- GRAD: Grade (weight without metric change)\n- CASL: Casual (0 = formal, 1 = casual)\n- CRSV: Cursive (0 = upright, 1 = cursive)\n- MONO: Monospace (0 = proportional, 1 = monospace)\n- FILL: Fill (0 = outline, 1 = filled)\n- SOFT: Softness (corner rounding)\n- WONK: Wonky (0 = normalized, 1 = wonky)\n\n## CSS Mapping\nMaps to `font-variation-settings` property.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[78,45],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/FontVariation.purs","start":[78,23]},"title":"VariationAxis"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","FontVariation"],"VariationAxis"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[80,52],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/FontVariation.purs","start":[80,1]},"title":"eqVariationAxis"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","FontVariation"],"VariationAxis"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[81,5